Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_apply_c...l_output_delay(25.10)  timing_apply_c...l_output_delay(25.10)

Name
       timing_apply_check_derate_to_external_output_delay

Syntax
       timing_apply_check_derate_to_external_output_delay

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Applies check derate to output external delay.

       The  set_timing_derate  -cell_check parameter by default does not apply
       check derate to output external delay (e.g., set_ouput_delay).  To  en-
       able  this feature, you can set the timing_apply_check_derate_to_exter-
       nal_output_delay timing global variable to  true.  The  global  applies
       cell (check) derate to the top boundary port.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

